LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: %r%, %rand(when you return to your locker you might notice the fresh scent of roses. Because I've just had several pounds of fine Belgian chocolate imported and delivered to your homeroom)%.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: I... oh, thank you! That's so classy.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: My dear %gender(r,sir,madam)%. %rand(Your eyes are like...,Every time I see you I think of Paris in the...,The melodious tones of your dulcet voice recall to me the...)%

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Are you listening to yourself right now? Because you sound like a freak.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: My dear %r%, might I say how ravishing you're looking today? I'd like to offer you this gift certificate for 25 dollars off at Bordstrams.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Uhhh.... ummm... I.... gotta go.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Why %r%, %greeting%. I wonder if you received the package I had sent over to your home?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: You mean that one filled with all those expensive chocolates?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Ah, you got it. Did you enjoy them?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: They tasted like crap. I fed them to my dog.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Oh.... uh, just so you know, you shouldn't give chocolate to a dog. It's really bad for them.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: %shocked%.... you tried to poison my dog?! That's cold, man.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Hello, %r%. I was wondering if maybe you'd like to join me for an all expenses paid trip to %random(the waterpark,the state fair,Rollercoaster Heights)% this weekend? All of the funnel cake you can eat.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Yeah, very funny. You probably are just going to not show up, right?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Why would you think I'd do something like that?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Oh please, %i%. I heard all about that time when %toc1%. Leave me alone.

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Oh, uh, hey %r%.... I was thinking of getting a limo for the prom... would you like to share it with me?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Really, %i%? You think after that time when %toc1% I'd be willing to go to the prom with you?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Uh... I guess a jerk like me doesn't deserve to go to the prom with a %gender(r,nice-guy,sweet-girl)% like you.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Awww.... hey, I'm willing to give you a chance. I'll think about it, okay?

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: Really? %positiveadj%!
Why %r%, %greeting%. I was wondering if you'd care to join me for dinner sometime at %random(The Pasta Garden,The Bolshevik Steakhouse,OMG Mondays)%? It's unlimited breadsticks.

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: Oh! Uh, I just had lunch there with my family the other day...

LineOfDialogue.initiatorLine: But is there anyone in your family as good-looking as me?

LineOfDialogue.responderLine: No. No there is not. I'll be there.
